abstract: Adam Bryant Corner Office column features interview with Aileen Lee, founder and partner of Cowboy Ventures, who discusses her career and management technique.
lead_paragraph: Ms. Lee, founder and partner of the venture capital firm Cowboy Ventures, on the qualities she values in searching for promising entrepreneurs.

headline.main: Aileen Lee of Cowboy Ventures: Aim to See Beneath the Surface
